1
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hero!</font>

2
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hero!</font>

3
00:00:24,210 --> 00:00:25,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take me with you!</font>

4
00:00:25,900 --> 00:00:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move this thing! Now!</font>

5
00:00:35,430 --> 00:00:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am <i>never</i> traveling with you again!</font>

6
00:00:38,180 --> 00:00:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, don't be like that. 
You're making me sad.</font>

7
00:00:40,790 --> 00:00:43,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't even reached the mine yet.</font>

8
00:00:43,520 --> 00:00:47,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then stop making trouble every 
single day, you worthless hero!</font>

9
00:00:58,030 --> 00:00:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beautiful.</font>

10
00:00:59,530 --> 00:01:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It suits you well.</font>

11
00:01:01,070 --> 00:01:03,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think this is what you 
should wear on the big day.</font>

12
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think what I usually wear 
would be just fine, though...</font>

13
00:01:07,850 --> 00:01:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That won't do.</font>

14
00:01:09,620 --> 00:01:13,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your attire must befit 
the Aquaraine family.</font>

15
00:01:13,170 --> 00:01:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't this a bit too extravagant?</font>

16
00:01:17,350 --> 00:01:19,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You dislike it?</font>

17
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:26,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me. There's a visitor for milady.</font>

18
00:01:30,180 --> 00:01:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for waiting.</font>

19
00:01:32,220 --> 00:01:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to come without warning.</font>

20
00:01:34,060 --> 00:01:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to ask you something 
about healing magic...</font>

21
00:01:38,310 --> 00:01:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, why are you dressed like that?</font>

22
00:01:41,290 --> 00:01:43,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks weird, doesn't it?</font>

23
00:01:43,490 --> 00:01:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not! You look super pretty.</font>

24
00:01:46,750 --> 00:01:52,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just surprised because I so 
rarely see you dressed like a noble.</font>

25
00:01:53,260 --> 00:01:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have an arranged marriage meeting.</font>

26
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, I see.</font>

27
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:59,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, what?!</font>

28
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you serious?! I mean, 
are you... sure about this?</font>

29
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:07,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm only meeting him once 
per His Majesty's orders.</font>

30
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:09,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't intend to marry him.</font>

31
00:02:09,550 --> 00:02:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still training, after all.</font>

32
00:02:12,510 --> 00:02:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Training? How studious can you be?</font>

33
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:18,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So when are you meeting the guy?</font>

34
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In three days.</font>

35
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is he?</font>

36
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's someone you know.</font>

37
00:02:24,490 --> 00:02:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A member of the hero's party 
of the Duchy of Luminaria.</font>

38
00:02:28,500 --> 00:02:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am honored to have 
this audience with you.</font>

39
00:02:33,260 --> 00:02:36,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is Soleil Graceheart.</font>

40
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:12,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Cecilia.</font>

41
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good to see you again.</font>

42
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:24,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe the last time we met</font>

43
00:04:24,490 --> 00:04:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">was at the party celebrating 
the defeat of the Demon King.</font>

44
00:04:27,860 --> 00:04:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, I believe so.</font>

45
00:04:31,890 --> 00:04:33,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">King Dartz told me</font>

46
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that you aren't interested in marriage</font>

47
00:04:37,110 --> 00:04:39,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and have turned down 
all proposals thus far.</font>

48
00:04:42,450 --> 00:04:45,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still training, after all.</font>

49
00:04:48,930 --> 00:04:50,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are fine tea leaves.</font>

50
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

51
00:04:52,090 --> 00:04:55,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's because you 
defeated the Demon King</font>

52
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:58,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that we can enjoy such delicious tea now.</font>

53
00:04:59,030 --> 00:05:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't me. It was all the hero.</font>

54
00:05:02,850 --> 00:05:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm sure he'd say it was 
all of us who made it possible.</font>

55
00:05:08,340 --> 00:05:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True.</font>

56
00:05:09,300 --> 00:05:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's probably why he was 
able to become a true hero.</font>

57
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said...</font>

58
00:05:14,980 --> 00:05:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there are some heroes</font>

59
00:05:16,910 --> 00:05:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">who are chosen to challenge the Demon 
King solely for their strength.</font>

60
00:05:21,570 --> 00:05:25,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know about Miller, the hero 
of the Gallis Empire, yes?</font>

61
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:26,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

62
00:05:27,330 --> 00:05:29,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is only a rumor,</font>

63
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I hear he's imprisoned 
in the empire now.</font>

64
00:05:32,990 --> 00:05:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a shame.</font>

65
00:05:35,300 --> 00:05:39,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So why does each nation 
have its own hero's party?</font>

66
00:05:39,450 --> 00:05:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you... no, anyone who's 
a noble must have an inkling.</font>

67
00:05:48,660 --> 00:05:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because even as humanity was 
being wiped out by demons,</font>

68
00:05:52,460 --> 00:05:56,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the kings of each nation competed 
for supremacy in the aftermath.</font>

69
00:05:56,940 --> 00:06:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't people just work hand in hand?</font>

70
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel the same way.</font>

71
00:06:05,170 --> 00:06:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But thankfully, King Dartz is a wise man.</font>

72
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is quite concerned about the signs 
of conflict in our neighbor nations.</font>

73
00:06:14,130 --> 00:06:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That must be why he accepted my proposal.</font>

74
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

75
00:06:21,090 --> 00:06:23,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our marriage will make 
it known far and wide</font>

76
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:29,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that the Duchy of Luminaria and the 
Kingdom of Clariness are friends.</font>

77
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will keep any countries with 
malicious intentions in check.</font>

78
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:39,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Cecilia...</font>

79
00:06:40,370 --> 00:06:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please do me the honor of marrying me.</font>

80
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And then,</font>

81
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">let us guide this world 
toward peace together.</font>

82
00:06:53,550 --> 00:06:55,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Check this out.</font>

83
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you kidding me?</font>

84
00:06:56,730 --> 00:06:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is...</font>

85
00:07:02,340 --> 00:07:06,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We ran into a monster nest 
while we were mining.</font>

86
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so cute.</font>

87
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cute.</font>

88
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a real problem.</font>

89
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:15,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't risk using my pickaxe now.</font>

90
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why I asked an 
official to contact the hero.</font>

91
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:23,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you please do something 
about this without hurting them?</font>

92
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it! Leave this to us!</font>

93
00:07:28,980 --> 00:07:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think we should do, Yoki?</font>

94
00:07:31,930 --> 00:07:33,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you asking me?</font>

95
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one who accepted the 
quest with total confidence.</font>

96
00:07:37,180 --> 00:07:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep!</font>

97
00:07:38,310 --> 00:07:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You always give me good advice,</font>

98
00:07:41,820 --> 00:07:44,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I figured you'd have a 
good idea this time, too!</font>

99
00:07:45,250 --> 00:07:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dude.</font>

100
00:07:46,610 --> 00:07:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seriously have no ideas at all?!</font>

101
00:07:58,390 --> 00:08:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. This is all 
far too much for me.</font>

102
00:08:02,300 --> 00:08:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would seem you don't understand 
the significance of your own standing.</font>

103
00:08:08,350 --> 00:08:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I made some big talk, but I 
am still inexperienced myself.</font>

104
00:08:12,990 --> 00:08:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still training.</font>

105
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:18,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's put the marriage discussion 
aside for the moment.</font>

106
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:23,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The truth is, I've been staying 
in Minerva for some time now.</font>

107
00:08:24,230 --> 00:08:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm in the midst of learning about 
this country and its people.</font>

108
00:08:27,410 --> 00:08:30,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And... why is that?</font>

109
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobles such as you and I need to have 
an understanding of other countries.</font>

110
00:08:35,260 --> 00:08:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If more nations understood each 
other, more wars could be avoided.</font>

111
00:08:41,090 --> 00:08:44,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I ask this favor of you...</font>

112
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Any time that is convenient 
for you will do.</font>

113
00:08:48,220 --> 00:08:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you please...</font>

114
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">teach me more about this country?</font>

115
00:08:58,040 --> 00:08:59,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

116
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

117
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see that you have 
very good intentions.</font>

118
00:09:07,050 --> 00:09:10,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it will lead us to friendlier 
relations with the Duchy of Luminaria,</font>

119
00:09:10,820 --> 00:09:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would be happy to help.</font>

120
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I ask for your advice?</font>

121
00:09:22,330 --> 00:09:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, I guess.</font>

122
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:28,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's about Cecilia's arranged marriage...</font>

123
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:29,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

124
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you just say?!</font>

125
00:09:31,470 --> 00:09:33,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, you didn't know about it?</font>

126
00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so shocked that I went to see her...</font>

127
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia! You can't go through with 
an arranged marriage! Tell them no!</font>

128
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The king ordered me to.</font>

129
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:53,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just can't! Tell them 
you won't do it, Cecilia!</font>

130
00:09:53,730 --> 00:09:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuga, if you're going to throw a 
tantrum, do it in front of the king.</font>

131
00:10:01,770 --> 00:10:03,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want her to have 
an arranged marriage.</font>

132
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:06,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's with Soleil, no less.</font>

133
00:10:06,090 --> 00:10:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soleil?</font>

134
00:10:07,460 --> 00:10:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's in the hero's party 
of the Duchy of Luminaria.</font>

135
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's about as good with 
the sword as Raven.</font>

136
00:10:13,890 --> 00:10:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the heir to an influential lord, 
he's smart, he has impeccable manners...</font>

137
00:10:18,220 --> 00:10:21,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry. You'll have to try to 
finish the quest on your own.</font>

138
00:10:22,420 --> 00:10:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

139
00:10:23,670 --> 00:10:25,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki?</font>

140
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:45,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why... didn't she tell me?</i></font>

141
00:10:54,500 --> 00:10:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why?!</i></font>

142
00:11:11,150 --> 00:11:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can we help you, miss?</font>

143
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... I-Is Yuga...</font>

144
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mikana!</font>

145
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad you're here!</font>

146
00:11:20,690 --> 00:11:23,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was really stuck! I 
can't handle this alone!</font>

147
00:11:23,890 --> 00:11:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Alone? Where's the civilian?</font>

148
00:11:26,410 --> 00:11:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki just up and went back home.</font>

149
00:11:29,420 --> 00:11:30,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

150
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were talking about Cecilia's 
arranged marriage and—</font>

151
00:11:34,770 --> 00:11:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yuga! You knew about that?</font>

152
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, good! You knew about it, too!</font>

153
00:11:41,590 --> 00:11:44,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does he think he's going to do?</font>

154
00:11:51,470 --> 00:11:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the orphanage.</font>

155
00:11:54,490 --> 00:11:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Mother!</font>

156
00:11:57,460 --> 00:12:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I baked cookies for all of you today.</font>

157
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:01,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here they are.</font>

158
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay! Cookies!</font>

159
00:12:03,340 --> 00:12:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guys, you have to say thank 
you to the Holy Mother!</font>

160
00:12:06,260 --> 00:12:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Holy Mother!</font>

161
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you share them, okay?</font>

162
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:15,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

163
00:12:17,140 --> 00:12:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy Mother! Tell us a story!</font>

164
00:12:19,520 --> 00:12:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, I'd rather draw pictures!</font>

165
00:12:22,010 --> 00:12:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Easy, now. Remember to take turns.</font>

166
00:12:24,740 --> 00:12:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's eat the cookies first.</font>

167
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you, mister?</font>

168
00:12:29,130 --> 00:12:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the Holy Mother's helper.</font>

169
00:12:31,730 --> 00:12:33,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soleil!</font>

170
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:38,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true. I only hope 
there's some way I can help.</font>

171
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raise me up high!</font>

172
00:12:42,140 --> 00:12:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Up... high?</font>

173
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does that mean?</font>

174
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know?</font>

175
00:12:48,590 --> 00:12:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're a grown-up.</font>

176
00:12:50,210 --> 00:12:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's weird!</font>

177
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soleil, pick her up with both hands.</font>

178
00:12:57,220 --> 00:12:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me, then.</font>

179
00:12:59,750 --> 00:13:02,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now lift her up high.</font>

180
00:13:02,570 --> 00:13:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Like this?</font>

181
00:13:06,820 --> 00:13:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! I'm way up high!</font>

182
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lucky!</font>

183
00:13:11,090 --> 00:13:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me next!</font>

184
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:13,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then me!</font>

185
00:13:13,660 --> 00:13:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, please!</font>

186
00:13:15,540 --> 00:13:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, Soleil.</font>

187
00:13:18,530 --> 00:13:23,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tire yourself out, but could you 
please do the same for the others?</font>

188
00:13:25,850 --> 00:13:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

189
00:13:27,420 --> 00:13:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's take turns, then, shall we?</font>

190
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

191
00:13:40,620 --> 00:13:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soleil, thank you for your help. 
The children were delighted.</font>

192
00:13:45,740 --> 00:13:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not at all. I should thank you 
for the valuable experience.</font>

193
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had no idea children played that way.</font>

194
00:13:54,100 --> 00:13:57,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They don't in the Duchy of Luminaria?</font>

195
00:13:57,310 --> 00:13:58,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

196
00:13:59,490 --> 00:14:01,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As the heir to the Graceheart family,</font>

197
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:04,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I spent my childhood studying 
and training with the sword.</font>

198
00:14:05,540 --> 00:14:08,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I still study under my father every day.</font>

199
00:14:08,300 --> 00:14:11,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never have opportunities 
to interact with our people.</font>

200
00:14:11,690 --> 00:14:16,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So when I was chosen for the hero's party 
and set out to slay the Demon King,</font>

201
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">every little thing surprised me.</font>

202
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:21,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The other members laughed so loudly,</font>

203
00:14:21,490 --> 00:14:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they'd get angry, and they were so honest.</font>

204
00:14:24,580 --> 00:14:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Interacting with them directly made 
me want to protect them all the more.</font>

205
00:14:29,770 --> 00:14:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From the Demon King and from 
any struggles they may face.</font>

206
00:14:33,130 --> 00:14:35,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Protect them?</font>

207
00:14:37,140 --> 00:14:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that presumptuous of me?</font>

208
00:14:39,140 --> 00:14:42,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's how I've always 
tried to be, as well.</font>

209
00:14:42,990 --> 00:14:44,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And...</font>

210
00:14:45,070 --> 00:14:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have asked someone with 
great power for help at times.</font>

211
00:14:50,190 --> 00:14:55,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, though, he helps people in 
need without even being asked.</font>

212
00:14:55,570 --> 00:14:57,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He sounds wonderful.</font>

213
00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

214
00:14:59,610 --> 00:15:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to become worthy 
of standing by his side.</font>

215
00:15:06,810 --> 00:15:09,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a role model, as well.</font>

216
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do?</font>

217
00:15:12,530 --> 00:15:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

218
00:15:14,850 --> 00:15:17,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I guess we both still 
have a long way to go!</font>

219
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:19,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very true.</font>

220
00:15:22,050 --> 00:15:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for today,</font>

221
00:15:24,100 --> 00:15:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I hope you'll teach me more tomorrow 
about this country and its people.</font>

222
00:15:29,500 --> 00:15:31,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy to do anything I can.</font>

223
00:15:34,310 --> 00:15:35,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

224
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, then, see you tomorrow.</font>

225
00:15:42,260 --> 00:15:45,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What in the world am I doing?!</font>

226
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:51,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just... couldn't turn him down...</font>

227
00:15:58,950 --> 00:16:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm working hard as an adventurer 
now, and once I make a decent living,</font>

228
00:16:03,770 --> 00:16:06,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm planning to ask her again, so...</font>

229
00:16:11,030 --> 00:16:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yoki seems to be having a lot of fun 
now that he's made so many friends.</i></font>

230
00:16:16,090 --> 00:16:20,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's not the same Yoki who couldn't 
leave the Demon King's castle.</i></font>

231
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:24,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm sure... he doesn't 
feel the same about...</i></font>

232
00:16:35,460 --> 00:16:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll make myself invisible 
and go straight to her!</i></font>

233
00:16:40,130 --> 00:16:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanish Wave!</font>

234
00:16:52,900 --> 00:16:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blue fire?</font>

235
00:16:55,180 --> 00:16:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yah!</font>

236
00:17:14,420 --> 00:17:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't expecting to run 
into a demon on my patrol.</font>

237
00:17:17,980 --> 00:17:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you trying to hunt humans 
down under cover of night?</font>

238
00:17:21,110 --> 00:17:23,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?!</font>

239
00:17:23,220 --> 00:17:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am...</font>

240
00:17:25,450 --> 00:17:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the Beast of Blue Fire!</font>

241
00:17:29,040 --> 00:17:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}BEAST OF BLUE FIRE</font>

242
00:17:30,730 --> 00:17:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Beast of... Blue Fire?</font>

243
00:17:34,130 --> 00:17:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I incinerate evil with 
the flames of justice!</font>

244
00:17:40,010 --> 00:17:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have time for you right now!</font>

245
00:17:42,830 --> 00:17:45,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why bother showing up here now, demon?!</font>

246
00:17:54,730 --> 00:17:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What am I even gonna do when I see her?</font>

247
00:17:57,870 --> 00:17:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will not escape!</font>

248
00:18:05,150 --> 00:18:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He erased it?!</font>

249
00:18:07,190 --> 00:18:08,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?!</font>

250
00:18:09,080 --> 00:18:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the guy on the wanted posters!</font>

251
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, isn't that a demon?</font>

252
00:18:13,570 --> 00:18:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a demon!</font>

253
00:18:15,490 --> 00:18:16,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's it doing here?!</font>

254
00:18:18,780 --> 00:18:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! Don't let that 
demon take one step into Minerva!</font>

255
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get lost!</font>

256
00:18:24,760 --> 00:18:25,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn demon!</font>

257
00:18:25,210 --> 00:18:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What'd you come here for?!</font>

258
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:51,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">C-Come in.</font>

259
00:18:53,290 --> 00:18:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pardon me.</font>

260
00:18:56,390 --> 00:19:00,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milady, my husband showed me this.</font>

261
00:19:14,220 --> 00:19:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did I have to reincarnate as a demon?</font>

262
00:19:22,950 --> 00:19:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is one of Kramen's...</font>

263
00:19:30,260 --> 00:19:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

264
00:19:37,220 --> 00:19:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is... Yoki?</font>

265
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Magic Swordsman of Black 
Lightning... on a wanted poster?!</font>

266
00:19:48,870 --> 00:19:52,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A demon attempted to infiltrate 
Minerva last night.</font>

267
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:55,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thankfully, we fought it off,</font>

268
00:19:55,100 --> 00:19:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we will increase 
patrols and remain alert.</font>

269
00:19:58,100 --> 00:20:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay focused, all of you!</font>

270
00:20:01,170 --> 00:20:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that concludes our captain's speech.</font>

271
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

272
00:20:05,340 --> 00:20:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Opening the gate!</font>

273
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shouldn't we check each 
of them individually?</font>

274
00:20:17,670 --> 00:20:21,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The demon that showed 
up had horns and wings.</font>

275
00:20:21,270 --> 00:20:24,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyone who doesn't appear 
obviously suspicious is fine.</font>

276
00:20:31,080 --> 00:20:32,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's...</font>

277
00:20:32,360 --> 00:20:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki?!</font>

278
00:20:37,170 --> 00:20:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia?!</font>

279
00:20:39,070 --> 00:20:40,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Cecilia.</font>

280
00:20:40,260 --> 00:20:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soleil?</font>

281
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I imagining it, or is he...</i></font>

282
00:20:44,630 --> 00:20:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... it's all right!</font>

283
00:20:47,710 --> 00:20:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know him!</font>

284
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you get hurt?!</font>

285
00:20:59,010 --> 00:21:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold still, please!</font>

286
00:21:01,110 --> 00:21:01,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

287
00:21:06,360 --> 00:21:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened?</font>

288
00:21:11,260 --> 00:21:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you finished healing 
him, Miss Cecilia?</font>

289
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said that you know him.</font>

290
00:21:17,670 --> 00:21:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... I'm sorry. Yoki is...</font>

291
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:23,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a guy she knows in passing.</font>

292
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm an adventurer she's helped out a lot.</font>

293
00:21:27,290 --> 00:21:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cecilia is kind to everyone, after all.</font>

294
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:32,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She even helps a guy like me.</font>

295
00:21:34,430 --> 00:21:35,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

296
00:21:35,990 --> 00:21:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't introduced myself. 
I am Soleil Graceheart.</font>

297
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am hoping to become 
Miss Cecilia's fiancé.</font>

298
00:21:44,660 --> 00:21:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoki, um... I didn't tell 
you about this, but...</font>

299
00:21:48,280 --> 00:21:50,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for getting in the way 
of your marriage meeting.</font>

300
00:21:52,300 --> 00:21:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, have a good day.</font>

301
00:22:01,250 --> 00:22:05,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've had a bit of an incident. 
I'll need you to cooperate.</font>

302
00:22:05,470 --> 00:22:06,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

303
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:11,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Irene, stay on watch over here.</font>

304
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:14,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, sir!</font>

305
00:22:15,060 --> 00:22:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, I'm at my height 
of seriousness here.</font>

306
00:22:28,320 --> 00:22:31,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Translation: Rebecca Cottrill
Timing: Andy Ellis</font>

307
00:22:35,020 --> 00:22:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Editing: Ashley Barboza
Quality Control: Riley Dalton</font>

308
00:22:38,320 --> 00:22:41,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Translation Check: Rei Miyasaka</font>

